title: still no skin '=' just want some info
body: do I need to file a supp ticket on the 23? or will the event take longer?

replies.body: All the info is being provided and updated through our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  The gifts are still being sent out, just hang tight and you'll get the goods!
